GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
S 1
SENATE BILL 342
Short Title: Funds for New Siler City Fire Station. (Public)
Sponsors: Senator Murdock (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to: Rules and Operations of the Senate
March 20, 2025
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS FOR A NEW FIRE STATION IN SILER CITY.
3 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
4 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Office of State
5 Budget and Management the sum of five million dollars ($5,000,000) in nonrecurring funds for
6 the 2025-2026 fiscal year to provide a directed grant to Siler City for the construction of a new
7 fire station.
8 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
*S342-v-1*

